data.description: Welcome to the gated community of Portofino! This furnished 2 bedroom, 2 bathroom condo on the first floor offers the perfect blend of comfort and convenience. Featuring tile flooring, complemented by carpet in the bedrooms & living room for added warmth.The kitchen boasts granite counters and a partially open layout. Enjoy the luxury of a walk-in shower in one bathroom, while the other offers a relaxing bathtub for added comfort. You'll find everything you need right at your fingertips!Portofino provides a secure and tranquil environment with its gated and guarded entrance, and offers a range of amenities including 2 pools, 2 hot tubs, and an inviting outdoor picnic and bbq area. Assigned parking is available, and there's even guest and RV parking for added flexibility. Located just a few minutes from the Colorado River and the excitement of the nearby casinos, living in Laughlin offers a unique opportunity for snowbirds, river enthusiasts, or anyone simply seeking a peaceful retreat.
